{"id":29494783748,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG3gavBA","head_branch":"fix/DHIS2-21821-invalid-lastupdatedduration-silently-ignored","head_sha":"b520f1fe66e9311a3f7945e7c743b5b4309b8de1","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":51138,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: reject invalid/negative lastUpdatedDuration on dataValueSets export instead of silently ignoring it","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":79855841170,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASl8dvkg","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29494783748","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29494783748","pull_requests":[{"id":4068187484,"number":24470,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24470","head":{"ref":"fix/DHIS2-21821-invalid-lastupdatedduration-silently-ignored","sha":"13db568659ebb5cc827752afa9f3e0dc3b6a2b14","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"c3320e59d5bec49c56be7c49b497585e42695325","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-16T11:32:18Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T11:43:26Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-16T11:32:18Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29494783748/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29494783748/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/79855841170","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29494783748/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29494783748/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29494783748/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: reject invalid/negative lastUpdatedDuration on dataValueSets export instead of silently ignoring it\n\nDateUtils.getDuration() returns null on any parse failure (its regex requires\nunsigned digits, so negative durations like \"-5d\" never match), and\nDefaultDataExportService.decodeParams() called it unchecked, so a malformed or\nnegative lastUpdatedDuration was silently discarded - indistinguishable from\n\"not provided\". If it was the client's only time filter, this surfaced as the\nunrelated E2002 error instead of pointing at the actual problem; otherwise it\nwas dropped with no error at all.\n\nErrorCode.E2005 (\"Duration is not valid: `{0}`\") already exists for exactly\nthis and is used by the sibling DefaultCompleteDataSetRegistrationExchangeService\nfor its createdDuration parameter, but was never wired up here.\n\ndecodeParams() now throws ConflictException(E2005, rawValue) when\nlastUpdatedDuration is non-blank but fails to parse. lastUpdatedDuration=0d\nis deliberately left valid - it parses successfully (Duration.ZERO) and is a\nwell-defined (if narrow) \"as of right now\" filter, analogous to\nstartDate == endDate being a valid zero-width date range.\n\nVerified via mutation testing: temporarily disabled the new guard, confirmed\nonly the two negative-case tests failed (the 0d-is-valid test stayed green),\nthen restored. No regressions in DataExportServiceExportTest,\nDataValueServiceTest, or DataValueSetControllerTest.\n\nRelated to DHIS2-21821.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"b520f1fe66e9311a3f7945e7c743b5b4309b8de1","tree_id":"0416aa43e64b097e4e398b2441ee21aa2dece07a","timestamp":"2026-07-16T11:30:54Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5